<Class name="CM_EDIAction" id="ce8e273d-1afb-4159-8a7a-51841086f72a">
    <superclass name="CM_Object"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>
A keyword in an EDI file may trigger an action in the system.

If an action with the matching keyword is found the action will be carried out on the referenced container.

E.g.

EDI Container WXYZ3456789 has keyword AUDIT and WASH.

Lookup EDIAction with keyword AUDIT and add/remove stop/todoTask according to the EDIAction.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="edi"/>
